article_title: President Obama Is Skipping Nancy Reagans Funeral For SXSW
article_text:
Obama is going to be delivering a key note speech at SXSW this year instead of attending Nancy Reagan’s funeral. Michelle will going to the funeral. That means Obama gets to eat as much barbeque and smoke as many cigarettes as he wants while in Austin. Great timing, Nancy.

Read more at jezebel.
